subject: Re: [Read_Alphabet] help on new font
msgSnippet: ... Good idea, but I just checked and thorn is already taken. But Thoth is not! I think I ll go with Thoth. Paul
messageBody:
Paige Gabhart wrote:
>
>
> Paul:
>
> Since QS differentiates between the voiced and voiceless dental
> fricative by having separate symbols, which TO does not, why not name
> your new font "Thorn"?
>

Good idea, but I just checked and thorn is already taken. But Thoth is
not! I think I'll go with Thoth.

Paul
